            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "But would it make sense for omnicomplete to call `lsp.completion.enable(...,{autotrigger=false})` , and then use `.get()` ? What are the tradeoffs? The advantage is that we need less explanation, and the features work together in a more obvious way.",
            "created_at": "2026-06-03T10:10:42Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/40068#issuecomment-4611240849",
            "id": 4611240849,
